thread.title: TV | X Factor

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | X Factor
text: It's the start of the live shows tonight although this is not the ACTUAL live shows with all the trimmings. In a first for the X Factor, the contestants will be finding out if they have been put through into their judge's final three live from Wembley arena, and not in judges houses as was done previously. In one way it's cruel to leave them waiting so long, but in another, it's good they will be surrounded by their family and friends. We won't lie though, we are hoping for some Rylan style meltdown.
